core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"Sorry, po得太急, 冇proof read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f0a59de27e6b7d71ba4cc34abdaff91ee39679","tid":742673,"uid":128271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"美樂家 <br />\nsell 家居清潔、美顏飲品個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不停叫人入會 <br />\n吹到全世界有分店 <br />\n啲人仲特登去海外開會 影到幾大幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾個月又升總監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎黎去去都係同一枝歌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6271515ab65466db14468d8eea2adf284e7e36","tid":742673,"uid":14503,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"其實最有興趣係想知個D洗腦圑玩咩花臣<br />\n有冇過來人知可以爆料?"},{"pid":"ee8fcd7ada41098bd5ea7f232fcbd919a1908179","tid":742673,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T18:35:09.000Z","msg":"乜鬼日本還原水 o5ok?"},{"pid":"a922cabac713987fda7ec4df1f5b9ebd9235006e","tid":742673,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T18:37:08.000Z","msg":"願景村<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.invision.asia/discovery_40.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.invision.asia%2Fdiscovery_40.php&d=IwHK6%2BEuOSiVLW3YHtZVI7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b2c569c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.invision.asia/discovery_40.php</a>"},{"pid":"9471df0eeae822e04a0b4cfb6d7b51ecd718865d","tid":742673,"uid":97945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T18:43:31.000Z","msg":"最近聽過係香港搵人去法國幫手買名牌手袋<br />\n行程一星期包